  "title": "QUANTITY SURVEYOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for pre & post contract activities in Construction projects</li><li>Liaise with project, purchase and finance team to provide monthly project costing and revenue</li><li>Responsible to update and verify project and production database</li><li>Involve in project budgeting, specification, contract claim and settlement of final statement</li><li>Monthly progress claim and payment certification</li><li>Ensure documents are in line with Company SOP standard</li><li>Other QS duties as assigned</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least Bachelor’s Degree in Quantity Surveying or equivalent</li><li>At least 2 years of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li><li>Good numeracy management skill</li><li>Meticulous, analytical with strong problem-solving skills</li><li>Good team player and able to work independently with minimal supervision</li></ul>",
